
###Recon
What is Recon and why is it important?
Importance of performing recon and gather assets.

###Types of Recon.
Active 
Passive

###Passive Recon Sites
censys https://censys.io/
shodan https://shodan.io
securitytrails https://securitytrails.com/
spyse https://spyse.com/
waybackurls https://archive.org
commoncrawl https://commoncrawl.org/
hackertarget https://hackertarget.com/
wappanalyzer
builtwith

###Active Recon Tools
Fuzzing?! - ffuf 
Sublister - subdomains
Knockpy - subdomains
wafwoof - gather waf data
subjs - gather js files
linkfinder - extracting endpoints from JS files
Aquatone - Screenshots
dirb - content discovery
nmap - port scanning

